    <h1>Ravi järjepidevuse korraldamise volitus</h1>
    <div>Termin: ravi järjepidevuse korraldamise volitus (<i>continuity facilitator mandate</i>
      <a href="https://contsys.org/concept/continuity_facilitator_mandate" title="Vaata terminit contsys.org lehel" target="_blank">⧉</a>)</div>
    <div>Määratlus: tegevusvolitus, mis annab õiguse ja kohustuse jälgida ja koordineerida terviselõimede kaudu terviseküsimustega seotud ravivolitustes kirjeldatud ravi osutamist (<i>healthcare mandate assigning the right and obligation to monitor and coordinate the delivery of care described in those care period mandates related to healthcare matters linked by specific health threads</i>)</div>
    <div>Valdkond: <a href="../../domain/responsibility">vastutus (<i>responsibility</i>)</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div>Märkus 1: Beyond solely assuming the function described above, a continuity facilitator may also assume the function of a lead and/or coordinator of healthcare activities delivered to the subject of care<br>
                 (<i>Beyond solely assuming the function described above, a continuity facilitator may also assume the function of a lead and/or coordinator of healthcare activities delivered to the subject of care</i>)</div>
      <div>Märkus 2: A continuity facilitation can be fulfilled only if the involved healthcare actors have the information needed to perform their tasks in healthcare activities<br>
                 (<i>A continuity facilitation can be fulfilled only if the involved healthcare actors have the information needed to perform their tasks in healthcare activities</i>)</div>
      <div>Märkus 3: For continuity of care the continuity facilitator mandates for complete clinical processes are of special importance from the subject of care's perspective.<br>
                 (<i>For continuity of care the continuity facilitator mandates for complete clinical processes are of special importance from the subject of care's perspective.</i>)</div>
    </div>
